window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I wasn't always this adorable, badass superhero you see before you.&nbsp;</b></p> <p>Well, I was, but there was a shady side to me, a part of my past I don't like to talk about. And that's what led me to Supralines, the best superhero school in the Oram galaxy.&nbsp;</p> <p>What follows is a bit of insanity, a bit of love, and a bit of self-discovery. Join me, and I promise you won't regret it!</p>"; 
